# Tavily Search Agent

![Search](https://img.shields.io/badge/search-3D8BD3?style=flat&logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,)
![LLM](https://img.shields.io/badge/llm-E85D2E?style=flat&logo=data:image/svg+xml;base64,)
[![link to source code](https://img.shields.io/badge/Source%20Code-E8ECF1?style=flat&logo=data%3Aimage%2Fsvg%2Bxml%3Bbase64%%2BCjwvc3ZnPgo%3D)](https://github.com/fetchai/uAgents-official/agents/tavily-agent)

This agent uses the Tavily Search API to give you a list of results from a prompt with a focus on efficient, quick and persistent search results.

## Example input

```python
input = "What is a Fetch.ai agent?"
```

## Example output
